        "Ingestion: Consumption of moxidectin tablets prescribed for the treatment of parasitic infections.",
        "Dermal contact: Handling veterinary formulations or accidental skin exposure during administration to animals.",
        "Inhalation: Inhalation of aerosolized particles during the application of moxidectin-containing products, though this is less common."
